gifted /ˈɡɪftɪd/

1. ADJ Someone who is gifted has a natural ability to do something well. 有天赋的 

例： ...one of the most gifted players in the world. …世界上最有天赋的运动员之一。 

2. ADJ A gifted child is much more intelligent or talented than average. (儿童) 天资聪慧的 

例： ...a state programme for gifted children. …一项培养天才儿童的国家计划。

